room_title: Escape room "Lost Teddy" by Expedition Escape in Montgomeryville
room_description:
Your parents have gone out for supper and left your uncle to babysit you. He loves playing tricks, so he has hidden your favorite teddy bear somewhere in your room. Your parents should arrive home in approximately 30 minutes. You have to find Teddy and get to bed before you're grounded!
This room is for players aged 8-12. There must be at least one adult (18 years of age or older) in the room that counts as a player.
